{"tid":655011,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺連尼住呢個人真係好尾機！","createTime":"2018-05-06T06:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T14:40:02.000Z","uid":17606,"like":54,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb507c8f492b7414f4f9b493df3fba7d27a9282","tid":655011,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"樣：7.5-8/10 <br />\n幾靚仔 清秀feel 起碼屌打9成兒登仔先 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/211024_13cbea142cd38ce048f67ccf15227fbb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F211024_13cbea142cd38ce048f67ccf15227fbb.png&h=21d87101&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n身高：驟眼睇應該差唔多180 <br />\n<br />\n音樂：識得吉他 作曲<br />\n<br />\n科技：有IT知識同技術<br />\n<br />\n收入：按照兒登既名氣 廣告費同合作活動<br />\n一年收入約5000萬走唔甩<br />\n再平均分返都最少一千萬年薪<br />\n高過晒50k月薪既連登仔<br />\n<br />\n智商：有生意頭腦 識得把握機會轉為自己優勢<br />\n連登已經係全港最大論壇<br />\n<br />\n呢個人真係勁到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先 冇人想知再講"},{"pid":"b62bedffef95550fd032892ef95e2107a04b11c6","tid":655011,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"有無唱歌片睇下"},{"pid":"35af4c01b9311998ec1514e4677d426adfcebe5e","tid":655011,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T07:00:30.000Z","msg":"K"},{"pid":"0ba230820f70bcb43bddd9c00c30df905a21df14","tid":655011,"uid":55151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T07:01:41.000Z","msg":"收左幾錢？"},{"pid":"4e36df59193970c82fe2ccc4ed2850d24650e781","tid":655011,"uid":94828,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T07:03:13.000Z","msg":"可惜係狗嚟"},{"pid":"55545f2499d2c0f44a5cf1c3ee9492aea4a39752","tid":655011,"uid":22700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T07:07:44.000Z","msg":"連叔好尾機呀"},{"pid":"1d5339a73f6